1) This code has been done in local system.
2) to run the code you need to download the data from below site and give that downloaded path as mentioned in the code.
  "https://ieee-dataport.org/open-access/flame-dataset-aerial-imagery-pile-burn-detection-using-drones-uavs"
3) For classification: download 7(Training) and 8(Test) number of dataset.
4) For segmentation: download 9(Images) and 10(Masks) number of dataset.
